business.name: Konceited Hair Studio & Extensions
business.description:
Thank you for choosing me as your stylist! 
Located in Winter Park 
For hair orders  please go to www.konceitedhairstudio.com

I have been licensed for over 10 years and have recently relocated to Seminole County, Florida.
I pride myself on being a multicultural stylist and skilled in various aspects of hair. 
I specialize in extension weaving, thermal hair straightening, brow shaping and more. If there is anything you are looking to accomplish, I highly recommend you reaching out to me and we can come up with a plan for you to achieve your desired outcome.

I look forward to seeing you soon!

services.description:
Level up from your traditional silk press serviceÂ 

You will receive the same steps with the original silk press as well as a steam hydration treatment during your shampoo and condition process

Rinsed with cool water to seal in the hydrating agents. Then we follow the steps of the original silk press serviceÂ

business.booking_policy: Changes allowed up to 1 days before visit
business.deposit_policy:
This business enforces a cancellation policy on select services and reserves the right to charge a cancellation fee for any no-shows and late cancellations. Note that you may be considered a no-show if you are late for your scheduled appointment, and it is up to the business to decide whether the fee is applied.

The cancellation fee is only charged if you violate the terms of the cancellation policy. If you show up to the appointment on time or cancel before the deadline listed on your confirmation page, no cancellation fee is withdrawn from your account. As the fee is not charged for successful appointments, you will be expected to pay for your appointment in full once the service is completed.
